[02:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'So, the whole point of using this model is&nbsp; that it’s trained on much better captions,&nbsp;&nbsp; which means it understands prompts a lot better. The model is also really fast.&nbsp; And the best part is, it can generate&nbsp; high-quality images even on smaller GPUs.&nbsp;'

