AUDIO: 'Changing this value to Flux 2 should also work,&nbsp;&nbsp; but after updating, you&nbsp; should get this lens option.&nbsp; The turbo model is working with this&nbsp; workflow, so I will get the other model now.&nbsp;'

[02:41] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Both the models we saw earlier&nbsp; have a new variant now.&nbsp; The MX FP8 is smaller in size, and it&nbsp; is optimized for Blackwell cards, which&nbsp;&nbsp; means if you have the latest 5 thousand series&nbsp; cards, then this file should work great for you.'

[02:58] [scene:talk]
