AUDIO: 'detailed prompt, and all the prompts&nbsp; will be shared with the workflow.&nbsp; Total time taken was 135 seconds, where the&nbsp; turbo model gave the image within 10 seconds,&nbsp;&nbsp; and the base model took around&nbsp; 2 minutes to generate an image.&nbsp; A joyful robot chef in a futuristic&nbsp; kitchen, flipping pancakes mid-air with&nbsp;&nbsp;'

