AUDIO: 'My prompt was, “A giant holding&nbsp; a person in his hand and both the&nbsp;&nbsp; person are looking at each other.” Image generation models often&nbsp;&nbsp; get confused about the size of the&nbsp; subject with the objects around it.&nbsp;'

[06:03] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'I asked for a person, and the image&nbsp; generated was of a young kid. The image&nbsp;&nbsp; definitely shows that the model somehow managed. In this image, I wanted to check the reflections;&nbsp;&nbsp; it was fine, but the woman looks different&nbsp; in the image generated by the base model.&nbsp;'

[06:20] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'I thought of using the same&nbsp; image and adding details to it.&nbsp; So I made an image-to-image workflow,&nbsp; and my prompt is a highly detailed image.&nbsp; The result generated is of a different&nbsp; woman, because the denoise value here is 1.0.&nbsp;'

[06:35] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'The value should be somewhere&nbsp; around 25 or 30 percent. . So, it works. A detailed prompt&nbsp; should make this image perfect.&nbsp;'

[06:47] [scene:talk]
